  "text": "Acknowledging that scheduled maintenance is not able to prevent the risk of failure, financial allocation of the cost of failure should be considered when planning the maintenance approach. According to [CITATION_1] , breakdown may cause collateral damage in a particular system. Relatively, additional cost will be incurred for the failures occurred before the predetermined maintenance time.",
